  "prompt": "Who is Bruce Wayne?",
  "response": "Bruce Wayne is a fictional character from DC Comics, best known as the secret identity of the superhero Batman. Created by writer Bill Finger and artist Bob Kane, Batman first appeared in \"Detective Comics\" #27 in 1939. Bruce Wayne is a wealthy industrialist and philanthropist from the fictional Gotham City. Traumatized by witnessing the murder of his parents as a child, he dedicates his life to fighting crime, using his intellect, physical prowess, and an array of gadgets and technology. He operates primarily under the guise of Batman, a masked vigilante, to protect Gotham City from various criminals and supervillains.",
